 religious heroine. She was canonized in  1920 . More recent influences have included the American film actress  Joan Crawford  (  1908–77 , born  Lucille le Sueur ), the British actress  Joan Collins  (  b. 1933 ), the American comedienne  Joan Rivers  (  b. 1933 ), and the West Indian pop singer  Joan Armatrading  (  b. 1950 )."],"variants":[{"name":"John","meanings":["form of   John  , also used quite frequently in the English-speaking world. In Northern Ireland it is sometimes found as a variant of   Ewan ."]}]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1705189,"age":14,"year":"1259","julianDay":2180901,"title":"100 Years of Conflict Between England and France Ends","description":"Treaty of Paris was signed on December 4, 1259, which ended 100 years of conflict between England and France.","url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Treaty_of_Paris_(1259)","urlTitle":"Wikipedia - Treaty of Paris 1259","jurisdictionLevel":0}],"lifeSummary":"Joan Baseville was born about 1245, in England. She had at least 2 sons and 2 daughters with Gerard Salvain I. She died before 1290, in her hometown."},"et":{"about 1245–before 1290":"umbes 1245–enne 1290","1200–1271":"1200–1271","1226–1300":"1226–1300","1266–Female":"1266–Surnud","1271–Female":"1271–Surnud","–1296":"–1296","1245–1290":"1245–1290","1259":"1259","1226":"1226","1245":"1245","1300":"1300","1266":"1266","1200":"1200","1296":"1296","about 1245":"umbes 1245","1271":"1271","before 1290":"enne 1290","1290":"1290","England":"England","Harswell, Yorkshire, England":"Harswell, Yorkshire, England"},"fi":{"about 1245–before 1290":"noin 1245–ennen vuotta 1290","1200–1271":"1200–1271","1226–1300":"1226–1300","1266–Female":"1266–Kuollut","1271–Female":"1271–Kuollut","–1296":"–1296","1245–1290":"1245–1290","1259":"1259","1226":"1226","1245":"1245","1300":"1300","1266":"1266","1200":"1200","1296":"1296","about 1245":"noin 1245","1271":"1271","before 1290":"ennen vuotta 1290","1290":"1290","England":"England","Harswell, Yorkshire, England":"Harswell, Y